6 2.) The provision of this Right, with equality for all individuals, shall be subject to
7 appropriate legislation by the Great and General Court.
8 The roles, and decision-making of all personal physicians, hospital physicians, and all
9 other medical personnel, who are appropriately involved in the care of any individual, shall be
10 respected, according to all appropriate medical standards, laws, and regulations.
